    <abstract>
      <t>&lt;p&gt;This document defines a new BGP attribute, the Traffic Engineering attribute, that enables BGP to carry Traffic Engineering information.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;The scope and applicability of this attribute currently excludes its use for non-VPN reachability information. [STANDARDS-TRACK]&lt;/p&gt;</t>
